[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說聖佛母般若波羅蜜多經",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳法大師賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞：",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時，世尊在王舍城鷲峯山中，與大苾芻眾千二百五十人俱，并諸菩薩摩訶薩眾而共圍繞。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊即入甚深光明宣說正法三摩地。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，觀自在菩薩摩訶薩在佛會中，而此菩薩摩訶薩已能修行甚深般若波羅蜜多，觀見五蘊自性皆空。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者舍利子承佛威神，前白觀自在菩薩摩訶薩言：",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若善男子、善女人，於此甚深般若波羅蜜多法門，樂欲修學者，當云何學？",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，觀自在菩薩摩訶薩告尊者舍利子言：",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今諦聽，為汝宣說。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人，樂欲修學此甚深般若波羅蜜多法門者，當觀五蘊自性皆空。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名五蘊自性空耶？",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂即色是空，即空是色；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "色無異於空，空無異於色。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此一切法如是空相，無所生無所滅，無垢染無清淨，無增長無損減。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，空中無色，無受、想、行、識；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無眼、耳、鼻、舌、身、意；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b25_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無色、聲、香、味、觸、法；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b25_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無眼界無眼識界，乃至無意界無意識界；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無無明無無明盡，乃至無老死亦無老死盡；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無苦、集、滅、道；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無智，無所得，亦無無得。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是無得故，菩薩摩訶薩依般若波羅蜜多相應行故，心無所著亦無罣礙；",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以無著無礙故，無有恐怖，遠離一切顛倒妄想，究竟圓寂。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有三世諸佛依此般若波羅蜜多故，得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故，應知般若波羅蜜多是廣大明、是無上明、是無等等明，而能息除一切苦惱，是即真實無虛妄法，諸修學者當如是學。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今宣說般若波羅蜜多大明曰：",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「怛𭔞切身他引一句　唵引　誐帝引　誐帝引引二　播引囉誐帝引三　播引囉僧誐帝引四　󰂛提　莎引賀引五「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩，若能誦是般若波羅蜜多明句，是即修學甚深般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊從三摩地安詳而起，讚觀自在菩薩摩訶薩言：",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說，如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多當如是學，是即真實最上究竟，一切如來亦皆隨喜。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說此經已，觀自在菩薩摩訶薩并諸苾芻，乃至世間天、人、阿修羅、乾闥婆等一切大眾，聞佛所說，皆大歡喜，信受奉行。",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說聖佛母般若波羅蜜多經",
        "from": "T08n0257_001:0852c20_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]